, 
<figureCitation id="BE303B5D9E647F411D720C261B0D951F" captionStart="Figures 1–5" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figures 1 - 5. Diplotaxis balam sp. nov. 1 male habitus, dorsal view 2 male habitus, lateral view 3 aedeagus, dorsal view 4 aedeagus, lateral view 5 female habitus. Scale bars: 1 mm (1, 2, 5); 0.5 mm (3, 4)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.993.49434.figures1-5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/475352" pageId="0" pageNumber="35">5</figureCitation>
).
